
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>World Boxing Schedule</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    video.background {
      position: fixed;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      min-width: 100%;
      min-height: 100%;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      z-index: -1;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .overlay {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.85));
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .presented {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .presented img {
      height: 26px;
    }
    .description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #dddddd;
    }
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .buttons a {
      background: white;
      color: black;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      width: 280px;
    }
    .buttons a:hover {
      background: gold;
      color: black;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .description { font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .presented img { height: 20px; }
      .buttons a { width: 90%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <video class="background" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
    <source src="background.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
  </video>

  <div class="overlay">
    <h1>WORLD BOXING SCHEDULE</h1>
    <div class="presented">
      <span>PRESENTED BY</span>
      <img src="bupas gym logo.png" alt="Bupas Gym Logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="description">
      Расписание титульных боев WBA, WBC, WBO, IBF, а также статусные встречи, которые нельзя пропустить.<br/><br/>
      Ивенты Top Rank, PBC, RCC BOXING PROMOTIONS, MATCHROOM, IBA.PRO, QUEENSBERRY PROMOTIONS — в одном клике.<br/><br/>
      Наш календарь сам добавит все предстоящие поединки в твой Apple или Google Календарь.<br/><br/>
      Никакого поиска — только бокс.
    </div>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="boxingschedule.ics">Подписаться в Apple Calendar</a>
      <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/r?cid=https://bupasgym.github.io/boxingschedule/boxingschedule.ics" target="_blank">Подписаться в Google Calendar</a>
      <a href="boxingschedule.ics" download>Скачать календарь</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
